Text: Re Form of Letter of Credit Cc so much for your response I will be retiring effective August th and my replacement will be Ms Mara Alexander It has been a pleasure working with Enron and my best wishes for your personal and professional success in the future Best regards Marty Oelmann Reply Separator Subject Form of Letter of Credit Author TanaJones at admpomunixmime Date PM At the request of Sara Shackleton attached is our form of Letter of Credit See attached file SCHEDULE doc

ISDA Master Agrmnt btwn Enron North America Corp and Cargill Cc Sara Since Enron prepared the ISDA Master Agreement referenced above we do not have an electronic version on file Could you arrange to forward to me via email the Schedule Irrevocable Transferable Standby Letter of Credit Format Thank you for your assistance and I look forward to receiving it Regards Marty Oelmann
